ed flux from XRBs in the normal\ngalaxy population out to z~0.5, suggesting they may contribute significantly to\nthe overall ionizing radiation from galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 May 2022 18:00:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
