etected by an ICCD camera, leading to full-field\ntransverse reconstruction through a single axial acquisition sequence.\nInterestingly, our setup permits concurrent OCT and QOCT trace acquisition, the\nformer with greater counts and the latter with the benefit of quantum-conferred\nadvantages. We hope that our current results will represent a significant step\nforward towards the actual applicability of QOCT, e.g. in clinical settings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 May 2022 03:52:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 19:33:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
