foundly exploit the symmetries. We then\nshow that the FRG enables one to describe turbulence forced at large scale,\nwhich was not accessible by perturbative means. We expound the derivation of\nthe spatio-temporal behaviour of $n$-point correlation functions, and largely\nillustrate these results through the analysis of data from experiments and\ndirect numerical simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 May 2022 11:33:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 10:02:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-09"}
